      "value": "<p>As an action, you can reach into your @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.l9H7gLFhbj9XBfEu]{Alchemist's Satchel}, pull out a vial of acid, and hurl the vial at a creature or object within 30 feet of you. The vial shatters on impact. A creature must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or take a number of d6 equal to your proficiency bonus acid damage. An object automatically takes the damage, and the damage is maximized plus your artificer level.</p>",
